data.Name: LilyPichu
data.Bio: Lily Ki (born: November 20, 1991), better known online as LilyPichu, is an American YouTuber and Twitch streamer who makes a variety of content spanning from animations to music on her YouTube channel. On Twitch, Lily mainly streams League of Legends and Just Chatting content. She is also known for being a member of Offline TV. She has released a couple of compilation albums on her Bandcamp, known as the Lilies Series, of which there are five so far. Read more on Last.fm
